Subject: CDSA Job Fails
Solution_Comment__c:
a) After upgrade from NEA 11.5 to NEA 11.6, create a new CDSA job and it runs fine without error.

1) At some point since your upgrade from StealthAUDIT 11.5 to Netwrix Enterprise Auditor 11.6, your CDSA job started failing.

2) Today on a call with Josh and I, we made a new instance of your CDSA job called "CDSA1", we ran it without error and it generated the 3 PowerPoint presentation (*.pptx) files into your Groups_zCDSA folder (or therabouts).

3) You opened the "StealthAUDIT_CDSA_Template.pptx" (or "Netwrix_CDSA_Template.pptx" equivalent) on your laptop and the report was populated correctly to the best of our knowledge.
